data.text:
No Sex, Please, We're Skittish

Even though the station has hired her replacement, Roz is not ready to turn in her headphones; Martin gives Niles and Daphne tips on starting a family.

The Good Lawyer

Dr. Shaun Murphy seeks legal representation to help him win a case and puts his faith in a promising, young lawyer who has obsessive compulsive disorder.

A Man, a Plan and a Gal: Julia

Daphne and Niles plan a dinner party to make an important announcement, but Julia upstages them.

The Harassed

Frasier's anger and loose tongue land him in sexual harassment trouble with his hostile and arrogant new radio show partner (Felicity Huffman); Niles tries to treat patients from home.
